ed%20into%20an%20oxidizer%20tank%2C%20which%20burst.%20Though%20it%20won't%20reach%20the%20moon%2C%20the%20lander%20continues%20to%20collect%20data%20while%20it%20still%20has%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20time%20a%20private%20space%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-orbit-rocket-suffers-anomaly-satellites-fails-reach-orbit-uk-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexperienced%20an%20anomaly%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20engineers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20space%20companies%20that%20invest%20heavily%20in%20testing%20and%20robust%20software%20processes%20tend%20to%20be%20successful%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-how-spacex-changed-starship-mega-rocket-explosion-elon-musk-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elearn%20from%20their%20failures%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarthik%20Gollapudi%20is%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Sift%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20helps%20space%20companies%20analyze%20their%20data%20and%20automate%20tasks%2C%20and%20Jason%20Hunter%20is%20its%20lead%20mission%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gollapudi%20and%20Hunter%20don't%20know%20how%20Astrobotic%20tests%20its%20vehicles%2C%20Gollapudi%20said%20the%20reason%20he%20started%20Sift%20was%20because%20of%20issues%20he%20saw%20across%20the%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20would%20build%20and%20test%20the%20propulsion%2C%20solar%20array%2C%20and%20other%20systems%20separately%2C%20then%20test%20them%20all%20together%20when%20the%20vehicle%20was%20fully%20assembled.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20sometimes%20you%20run%20into%20mistakes%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20SpaceX%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20culture%20was%2C%20you%20need%20to%20integrate%20these%20things%20all%20together%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Gollapudi%20said.%20Then%20the%20engineers%20would%20run%20hundreds%20of%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20doing%20at%20Sift%20is%20making%20it%20so%20the%20whole%20data%20review%20is%20automated%20into%20rules%20that%20are%20running%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Gollapudi%20said.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20said%2C%20companies%20tend%20to%20leave%20long%20gaps%20between%20tests%20because%20the%20review%20process%20is%20so%20lengthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20test%2C%20you're%20introducing%20risk%20to%20your%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Gollapudi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20Astrobotic%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20the%20company%20said%20it%20is%20not%20providing%20additional%20statements%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPrepping%20for%20lunar%20launch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20prepare%20for%20a%20mission%2C%20Hunter%20said%20he%20would%20expect%20a%20company%20to%20run%20simulations%20of%20every%20device%2C%20create%20a%20hybrid%20setup%20with%20real%20and%20simulated%20hardware%2C%20and%20then%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20simulations%20and%20hardware%20tests%20matched%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX%20engineers%20would%20also%20simulate%20different%20types%20of%20failures%20to%20see%20how%20the%20whole%20system%20reacted%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20comprehensive%20suite%20of%20tests%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20determine%20how%20all%20the%20subsystems%20are%20interacting%20with%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-launch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eafter%20launch%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hunter%20said%20Sift%20could%20help%20companies%20quickly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-starship-launch-rocket-blows-up-explosion-elon-musk-mars-2023-11%5C%22%20ta