-Boeing-Launches-737-New-Engine-Family-with-Commitments-for-496-Airplanes-from-Five-Airlines%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EBoeing%20would%20modify%20the%20737%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20so%20it%20could%20take%20on%20larger%20engines%20and%20be%20more%20fuel%20efficient%20like%20Airbus'%20new%20model%20that%20was%20taking%20market%20share%20at%20the%20time.%20The%20similarities%20also%20kept%20both%20maintenance%20and%20pilot%20training%20as%20easy%20and%20as%20cheap%20for%20its%20airline%20customers%20already%20operating%20older%20737%20planes%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20bigger%20engines%20tipped%20the%20delicate%20balance%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20so%20Boeing%20created%20a%20self-stabilizing%20system%20to%20compensate%20known%20as%20MCAS%20intended%20to%20make%20the%20plane%20fly%20like%20the%20older%20models.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fboeing-charged-737-max-fraud-conspiracy-and-agrees-pay-over-25-billion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20investigators%20say%20Boeing%20then%20hid%20MCAS's%20existence%20by%20omission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20FAA%2C%20and%20subsequently%20all%20pilots%20who%20would%20fly%20the%20aircraft%2C%20as%20it%20was%20left%20out%20of%20training%20documentation%20and%20the%20manual.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInfamously%2C%20the%20MCAS%20system%20has%20been%20blamed%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20346%20people%20involved%20in%20two%20Max%20crashes%20in%202018%20and%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20made%20mistakes%20and%20we%20got%20some%20things%20wrong.%20We're%20improving%20and%20we're%20learning%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN1X810X%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EBoeing%20CEO%20Dennis%20Muilenburg%20told%20members%20