%20be%20out%20of%20jail%2C%20he%20moves%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds%20and%20stays%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Whenever%20there%20is%20an%20argument%20on%20the%20bail%20in%20the%20court%2C%20he%20falls%20unconscious%2C%20which%20is%20a%20strange%20coincidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Jain's%20counsel%20called%20the%20submission%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20hearing%20remained%20inconclusive%20today%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20and%20Justice%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20listed%20the%20matter%20for%20January%2017%20after%20Jain's%20counsel%20concluded%20their%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Jain's%20interim%20bail%20will%20remain%20extended%20until%20further%20orders%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20ED%2C%20took%20the%20court%20through%20allegations%20against%20Satyendar%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20SV%20Raju%20apprised%20the%20court%20about%20the%20unaccounted%20cash%20received%20by%20the%20companies.%20ASG%20apprised%20the%20court%20that%20JP%20Mohta%20was%20his%20chartered%20accountant%20who%20was%20looking%20after%20these%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20said%20the%20ED%20case%20is%20that%20Jain%20wanted%20to%20convert%20cash%20into%20white%20and%20hence%20he%20told%20Mohta%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20says%20Jain%20has%20told%20Mohta%20that%20he%20knows%20some%20Calcutta%20operators%20who%20have%20shell%20companies%20that%20will%20give%20you%20entries%20if%20you%20give%20them%20cash%2C%20maybe%20even%20charge%20a%20little%20commission%20and%20give%20you%20interest%20and%20that%20money%20will%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASG%20SV%20Raju%20informed%20the%20SC%20that%20the%20price%20of%20these%20shares%20was%20inflated%20so%20that%20more%20money%20could%20come%20and%20fewer%20shares%20could%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mithal%20wanted%20to%20know%20how%20this%20would%20help%20Satyendar%20Jain.%20To%20which%20ASG%20SV%20Raju%20replied%20that%20it%20would%20help%20Jain%20convert%20this%20money%20into%20white%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20hearing%20on%20Jain's%20bail%20witnessed%20many%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20December%202023%2C%20as%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20explained%20why%20the%20matter%20was%20listed%20before%20a%20different%20combination%20of%20the%20bench%20as%20there%20was%20a%20matter%20relating%20to%20the%20extension%20of%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20also%20mentioned%20the%20communication%20received%20from%20Justice%20AS%20Bopanna%20to%20take%20up%20part%20of%20heard%20matter%20from%20him%20because%20he%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20hear%20the%20matter%20due%20to%20medical%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Jain's%20bail%20plea%20was%20partly%20heard%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20AS%20Bopanna%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi.%20Later%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20listed%20before%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Trivedi%20and%20Justice%20Satish%20Chandra%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20underwent%20surgery%20on%20July%2021.%20The%20interim%20bail%20given%20to%20Jain%20on%20medical%20grounds%20is%20extended%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2026%2C%20the%20top%20court%20granted%20interim%20bail%20to%20Satyendar%20Jain%20for%20six%20weeks%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20but%20imposed%20various%20conditions%2C%20including%20refusing%20to%20talk%20with%20the%20media%20or%20leaving%20Delhi%20without%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatyendar%20Jain%20has%20moved%20to%20the%20top%20court%20seeking%20bail%20in%20money%20laundering%20cases.%20He%20has%20challenged%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20order%20dismissing%20his%20bail%20plea%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%206%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20Satyendra%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%2C%20while%20dismissing%20the%20Satyendar%20Jain%20bail%20plea%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20applicant%20is%20an%20influential%20person%20and%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20tamper%20with%20evidence.%20Satyender%20Jain%2Fapplicant%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20can't%20be%20held%20to%20clear%20the%20twin%20conditions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20had%20kept%20the%20order%20reserved%20for%20March%2021%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20submissions%20made%20by%20the%20defence%20and%20prosecution%20sides%20after%20multiple%20hearings.%20During%20arguments%20in%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20SV%20Raju%20appeared%20for%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20contented%20that%20money%20laundering%20is%20crystal%20clear%20against%20Jain%20and%20other%20co-accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20bail%20plea%2C%20Jain%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20appeared%20before%20the%20ED%20on%20seven%20occasions.%20I%20have%20cooperated%20and%20participated%20in%20the%20investigation.%20I%20was%20arrested%20five%20years%20down%20the%20line%20in%202022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2017%2C%202022%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20dismissed%20the%20bail%20petition%20of%20Satyendar%20Jain.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20May%2030%2C%202022%2C%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20is%20presently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20case%20is%20based%20on%20a%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20complaint%20registered%20on%20the%20allegation%20that%20Satyendar%20Jain%20had%20acquired%20movable%20properties%20in%20the%20name%20of%20various%20persons%20from%20February%2014%2C%202015%2C%20to%20May%2031%2C%202017%2C%20which%20he%20could%20not%20satisfactorily%20account%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3