partment%20secretary%20N%20Kheda%20Varta%20Singh%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20IIT%20Guwahati%20director%20Parameswar%20K%20Iyer.%20A%20team%20from%20IIT-Guwahati%20is%20also%20coming%20to%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Heavy-oil%20leak%20in%20Manipurs%20Leimakhong%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Heavy-oil%20leak%20in%20Manipurs%20Leimakhong%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9rc50g98_leimakhong-oil-fire_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy-oil%20leak%20in%20Manipur's%20Leimakhong%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20in%20Kanto%20Sabal%20village%2C%20some%204%20km%20from%20the%20power%20plant%2C%20found%20a%20layer%20of%20a%20viscous%2C%20black%20substance%20running%20in%20Leimakhong%20river%20towards%20Kanto%20dam%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20The%20alarmed%20residents%20scooped%20up%20the%20greasy%20substance%20with%20buckets%20and%20found%20them%20smelling%20of%20oil%2C%20which%20they%20found%20also%20burned%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residents%20contacted%20the%20authorities%2C%20after%20which%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20coordination%20in%20recent%20times%20the%20power%2C%20water%20resources%2C%20environment%20and%20disaster%20relief%20departments%2C%20along%20with%20the%20police%20and%20the%20district%20administration%20rushed%20to%20the%20area%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20officers%20who%20reached%20the%20river%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20was%20Dr%20T%20Braj%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20director%20of%20Environment%20and%20Climate%20Change.%20%26quot%3BState%20government%20officials%20in%20cooperation%20with%20residents%20and%20state%20security%20managed%20to%20divert%20the%20contaminated%20river%20into%20nearby%20wastelands%20and%20unused%20lands%2C%20and%20blocked%20much%20of%20the%20flow%20from%20going%20downstream%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone%20from%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20most%20of%20the%20viscous%20layer%20of%20oil%20has%20been%20cleared%2C%20though%20in%20this%20season%20the%20water%20level%20is%20low%2C%20and%20the%20flow%20is%20not%20strong.%20%26quot%3BSome%20residual%20amount%20will%20remain.%20We%20will%20get%20to%20know%20more%20soon%20as%20the%20results%20of%20the%20samples%20being%20tested%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Singh%2C%20a%20top%20expert%20on%20environment%20issues%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20who%20has%20experience%20in%20the%20COP%20climate%20summit%20talks.%20He%20said%20he%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20night%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20most%20part%20of%20the%20day%20on%20Thursday%20near%20the%20river%2C%20collecting%20samples%2C%20directing%20teams%20and%20working%20with%20the%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Manipur%20government%20is%20taking%20samples%20from%20the%20Leimakhong%20river%20and%20testing%20them%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Manipur%20government%20is%20taking%20samples%20from%20the%20Leimakhong%20river%20and%20testing%20them%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Foq8sj75g_leimakhong-oil-leak_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20is%20taking%20samples%20from%20the%20Leimakhong%20river%20and%20testing%20them%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20said%20the%20course%20of%20the%20stream%20has%20been%20blocked%20and%20diverted%20to%20a%20nearby%20dugout%20field%20at%20Kanto%20Sabal%20to%20contain%20the%20spread%20of%20contaminants%20into%20the%20public%20water%20supply%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PHED's%20initial%20reports%20say%20there%20is%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20drinking%20water%20supply%20system.%20The%20PHED%20has%2C%20however%2C%20as%20a%20precaution%20temporarily%20closed%20the%20water%20supply%20schemes%20located%20near%20the%20streams%2C%20and%20will%20re-open%20them%20once%20the%20test%20samples%20confirm%20the%20water%20is%20safe%20to%20drink.%20The%20government%20said%20it%20has%20arranged%20drinking%20water%20by%20boring%20tube%20wells%20and%20sending%20water%20tankers%20to%20the%20affected%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20said%20residents%20who%20need%20drinking%20water%20may%20call%20these%20helplines%20-%208794006422%2C%207085922914.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20police%20will%20run%20their%20own%20investigation%20separate%20from%20the%20committee%20formed%20by%20the%20Governor%20into%20how%20the%20leak%20happened%2C%20publicly%20available%20information%20throws%20up%20several%20questions%20as%20to%20the%20location%20of%20the%20heavy-fuel%20power%20plant%20and%20its%20distance%20to%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pic%201%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pic%201%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpgga1sh8_leimakhong-oil-fire_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPic%201.%20High-resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fr7pia6mg_leimakhong_625x300_11_January_24.png%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearest%20point%20from%20the%20power%20station%20to%20the%20river%20%3Cstrong%3E(pic%201)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20450%20metres%2C%20while%20the%20farthest%20point%20is%202.5%20km%20within%20Leimakhong.%20There%20are%20buildings%2C%20school%2C%20church%2C%20market%20and%20other%20structures%20between%20the%20river%20and%20the%20power%20plant.%20A%20surface%20oil%20leak%20would%20have%20contaminated%20the%20areas%20between%20the%20river%20and%20the%20power%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20electrical%20engineer%20who%20has%20been%20to%20this%20power%20plant%20while%20it%20was%20operational%20said%20the%20facility%20is%20a%20self-contained%20unit%2C%20with%20no%20fuel%20connection%20outside%20except%20the%20electricity%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20specifically%20told%20by%20the%20electrical%20engineer%20and%20another%20civil%20engineer%20that%20no%20piping%20goes%20out%20of%20the%20compound%2C%20and%20heavy%20fuel%20is%20stored%20inside%20the%20compound.%20Oil%20tankers%20from%20Assam%20and%20other%20areas%20used%20to%20bring%20heavy%20fuel%20to%20fill%20the%20tanks%20in%20the%20compound.%20For%20example%2C%20those%20storage%20tanks%20were%20like%20the%20ones%20in%20any%20fuel%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20engineer%20who%20has%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20ruled%20out%20underground%20seepage%20from%20the%20storage%20unit%20as%20the%20residual%20heavy%20oil%20from%20the%20defunct%20power%20station%20was%20not%20enough%20in%20volume%20to%20push%20through%20the%20soil%20till%20the%20river.%20The%20tank%20would%20also%20act%20as%20a%20shield%20against%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pic%202%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pic%202%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhh464tq_leimakhong-oil-fire_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPic%202.%20High-resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F16hmhjco_leimakhong_625x300_11_January_24.png%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20reference%2C%20the%20tree%20%3Cstrong%3E(pic%202)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20shows%20the%20road%20towards%20the%20general%20direction%20of%20Leimakhong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pic%203%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pic%203%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fk1pvi9qo_leimakhong-oil-fire_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPic%203.%20High-resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fsc6g769_leimakhong_625x300_11_January_24.png%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20above%20%3Cstrong%3E(pic%203)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20shows%20the%20location%20of%20the%20power%20station.%20Notice%20the%20tree%20on%20the%20left%20for%20distance%20and%20direction%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pic%204%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pic%204%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6ke7ad88_kantal-sabal_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPic%204.%20High-resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7uqtlmp_leimakhong_625x300_11_January_24.png%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20above%20%3Cstrong%3E(pic%204)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20shows%20Kanto%20Sabal%20village%20and%20Kanto%20dam%2C%20where%20residents%20first%20saw%20the%20contaminated%20water.%20The%20white%20arrows%20show%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20river's%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pic%205%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pic%205%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fggg2ho1o_leimakhong-oil_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPic%205.%20High-resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F81lhn82o_leimakhong_625x300_11_January_24.png%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20image%20%3Cstrong%3E(pic%205)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20shows%20the%20entire%20area%20-%20(left%20to%20right)%20Leimakhong%20hills%20visible%20from%20the%20tree%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20river%2C%20the%20power%20plant%20and%20its%20distance%20from%20the%20river%2C%20the%20road%20to%20Leimakhong%20from%20the%20tree%2C%20Kanto%20Sabal%20village%20and%20dam%2C%20and%20the%20tree%20for%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20tensions%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20persist%20eight%20months%20since%20May%202023%2C%20when%20violence%20broke%20out%20after%20the%20Kukis'%20protest%20against%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes'%20(ST)%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Boil%20leak%26quot%3B%20amid%20the%20Manipur%20tension%20makes%20the%20matter%20extremely%20sensitive%2C%20since%20people%20from%20different%20communities%20live%20in%20the%20affected%20area%20downstream%2C%20and%20the%20area%20around%20the%20defunct%20power%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnature-of-violence-changed-to-security-forces-vs-insurgents-manipur-chief-minister-n-biren-singh-to-ndtv-4823360%5C%22%3Etold%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%208%20that%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20due%20to%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20has%20now%20changed%20into%20a%20situation%20where%20insurgents%20are%20attacking%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20these%20past%20eight%20months%2C%20unwanted%20incidents%20took%20place%20on%20some%20days%2C%20not%20for%20the%20whole%20eight%20months.%20Three-four%20months%20were%20peaceful%20and%20silent.%20The%20violence%20during%20the%20new%20year%20was%20between%20the%20state%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%2C%20not%20between%20two%20communities.%20Now%2C%20the%20dimension%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20changed%20to%20state%20forces%20fighting%20against%20militants%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704999000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0uq2nc68_leimakhong-power-plant-map_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleimakhong-manipur-heavy-oil-leak-accident-or-sabotage-some-unanswered-questions-4844970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20unknown%20people%20a%20day%20after%20oil%20leaked%20into%20a%20river%20and%20streams%20from%20a%20defunct%20heavy-oil%20power%20station%20in%20Manipur's%20Leimakhong%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleimakhong-manipur-heavy-oil-leak-accident-or-sabotage-some-unanswered-questions-4844970%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleimakhong-manipur-heavy-oil-leak-accident-or-sabotage-some-unanswered-questions-4844970%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleimakhong-manipur-heavy-oil-leak-accident-or-sabotage-some-unanswered-questions-4844970%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fossil%20Found%20In%20US%20Represents%20New%20Dinosaur%20Species.%20See%20Pics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20reassessing%20a%20partial%20skull%20first%20unearthed%20in%201983%20in%20southeastern%20New%20Mexico%20have%20concluded%20that%20the%20fossil%20represents%20a%20new%20species%20of%20Tyrannosaurus%20-%20the%20fearsome%20apex%20predator%20from%20western%20North%20America%20at%20the%20twilight%20of%20the%20dinosaur%20age%20-%20that%20predated%20the%20fabulously%20famous%20T.%20rex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubtle%20differences%20from%20Tyrannosaurus%20rex%20observed%20in%20the%20skull%20merit%20recognizing%20the%20dinosaur%20as%20a%20separate%20species%20called%20Tyrannosaurus%20mcraeensis%20that%20lived%20several%20million%20years%20before%20T.%20rex%20and%20was%20comparable%20in%20size%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20skull%20previously%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20T.%20rex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20jaw%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20jaw%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkcepkdn_dinosaur-fossil_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jaw%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20researchers%20expressed%20doubt%20that%20it%20represents%20a%20new%20Tyrannosaurus%20species%2C%20saying%20differences%20between%20it%20and%20other%20T.%20rex%20skulls%20were%20unremarkable%20and%20the%20study's%20conclusion%20that%20the%20fossil%20dated%20to%2071-73%20million%20years%20ago%20was%20problematic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET.%20rex%20has%20been%20the%20sole%20species%20of%20the%20genus%20Tyrannosaurus%20recognized%20since%20the%20dinosaur%20was%20first%20described%20in%201905.%20A%20genus%20is%20a%20broader%20grouping%20of%20related%20organisms%20than%20a%20species.%20T.%20rex%20fossils%20date%20to%20the%20couple%20million%20years%20before%20an%20asteroid%20struck%20Earth%2066%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20dooming%20the%20dinosaurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20parts%20of%20the%20New%20Mexico%20skull%20were%20found%20near%20the%20base%20of%20Kettle%20Top%20Butte%20in%201983%2C%20with%20more%20later%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20teeth%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus%20mcraeensis.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20teeth%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus%20mcraeensis.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fl7elf378_dinosaur-fossil_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20view%20of%20teeth%20of%20the%20newly%20identified%20dinosaur%20species%20Tyrannosaurus%20mcraeensis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaleontologist%20Anthony%20Fiorillo%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20New%20Mexico%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20%26amp%3B%20Science%20and%20one%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Scientific%20Reports%2C%20said%20about%2025%25%20of%20the%20skull%20has%20been%20collected.%20Most%20of%20the%20braincase%20and%20the%20upper%20jaws%20are%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompared%20to%20T.%20rex%2C%20the%20lower%20jaw%20is%20shallower%20and%20more%20curved%20towards%20the%20back.%20The%20blunt%20hornlets%20above%20the%20eyes%20are%20lower%20than%20in%20T.%20rex%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20paleontologist%20Nick%20Longrich%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Bath%20in%20England%2C%20another%20of%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20nature%20of%20species%20that%20the%20differences%20tend%20to%20be%20subtle.%20The%20key%20thing%20is%20they're%20consistent.%20We%20looked%20at%20lots%20of%20different%20T.%20rex%2C%20and%20our%20animal%20was%20consistently%20different%20from%20every%20known%20T.%20rex%2C%20in%20every%20bone%2C%26quot%3B%20Longrich%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20the%20differences%20involve%20important%20traits.%20Fiorillo%20noted%20that%20the%20feature%20above%20the%20Tyrannosaurus%20eyes%20has%20been%20interpreted%20as%20important%20in%20sexual%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20these%20differences%20imply%20that%20our%20animal%20ate%20differently%20and%20may%20have%20selected%20mates%20differently%20than%20the%20more%20famous%20Tyrannosaurus%20rex%2C%26quot%3B%20Fiorillo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyrannosaurus%20had%20a%20massive%20head%2C%20tremendous%20bite%20strength%2C%20walked%20on%20two%20strong%20legs%2C%20and%20had%20puny%20arms.%20Perhaps%20the%20largest-known%20T.%20rex%20is%20a%20specimen%20named%20Sue%20at%20the%20Field%20Museum%20in%20Chicago%2C%20at%2040-1%2F2%20feet%20(12.3%20meters)%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20the%20existence%20of%20T.%20mcraeensis%20changes%20the%20understanding%20of%20Tyrannosaurus%20origins.%20The%20researchers%20said%20T.%20mcraeensis%20was%20larger%20than%20other%20close%20Tyrannosaurus%20relatives%20inhabiting%20northern%20North%20America%20before%20T.%20rex%2C%20suggesting%20that%20giant%20species%20of%20this%20group%20evolved%20millions%20of%20years%20earlier%20than%20previously%20thought%20and%20came%20from%20southern%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaleontologist%20Thomas%20Carr%20of%20Carthage%20College%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20who%20has%20studied%20variation%20within%20T.%20rex%2C%20called%20the%20new%20study%20%26quot%3Bunpersuasive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20features%20in%20the%20New%20Mexico%20specimen%20that%20supposedly%20make%20it%20unique%20are%20seen%20among%20other%20T.%20rex%20fossils%2C%26quot%3B%20Carr%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20'differences'%20are%20not%20discrete%20and%20obvious%2C%20instead%20they%20are%20like%20shades%20of%20gray%20or%20shapes%20in%20clouds.%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20specimen%20myself%20several%20times%20and%20nothing%20leaps%20out%20to%20me%20as%20anything%20different%20from%20other%20T.%20rex%20adults.%20The%20differences%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20can%20be%20accounted%20for%20by%20relative%20maturity%20and%20individual%20variation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fossil%20was%20dated%20not%20based%20on%20the%20skull%20itself%20but%20on%20rock%20beneath%20it%2C%20Carr%20said.%20Existing%20evidence%20indicates%20Tyrannosaurus%20appeared%20no%20earlier%20than%2067%20to%2068%20million%20years%20ago%2C%20Carr%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20potential%20additional%20Tyrannosaurus%20species%20has%20been%20contentious.%20Some%20researchers%20in%202022%20proposed%20the%20existence%20of%20three%20Tyrannosaurus%20species%2C%20based%20on%20thighbone%20and%20tooth%20variations%20among%20fossils.%20Other%20researchers%20disagreed%2C%20seeing%20insufficient%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704998880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fl811dmuo_dinosaur-fossil_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fw