used%20by%20the%20gaming%20community%20to%20showcase%20live%20gameplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20many%20of%20you%20are%20wondering%20why%20this%20is%20happening.%20Over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20we've%20been%20working%20to%20build%20a%20more%20sustainable%20business%20so%20that%20Twitch%20will%20be%20here%20for%20the%20long%20run%20and%20throughout%20the%20year%20we%20have%20cut%20costs%20and%20made%20many%20decisions%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%2C%26quot%3B%20Clancy%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20it%20has%20become%20clear%20that%20our%20organization%20is%20still%20meaningfully%20larger%20than%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20the%20size%20of%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20at%20Prime%20Video%20and%20at%20the%20Amazon%20MGM%20Studio%20division%20were%20also%20described%20as%20painful%20but%20necessary%20to%20keep%20the%20businesses%20in%20line%20with%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20difficult%20decision%20to%20make%20and%20one%20that%20my%20leadership%20team%20and%20I%20do%20not%20take%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20entertainment%20chief%20Mike%20Hopkins%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20because%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20evolve%20quickly...it's%20important%20that%20we%20prioritize%20our%20investments%20for%20the%20long-term%20success%20of%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20bought%20the%20iconic%20MGM%20studio%20in%202022%2C%20merging%20it%20with%20its%20own%20production%20studio%20where%20content%20is%20primarily%20geared%20towards%20the%20Prime%20Video%20streaming%20service%2C%20a%20rival%20to%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%20Plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20company%20seeks%20to%20increase%20revenue%2C%20last%20month%20Amazon%20said%20that%20Prime%20Video%20subscribers%20would%20start%20seeing%20ads%20on%20their%20service%20on%20January%202