%2C%20as%20the%20present%20one%2C%20are%20those%20where%20the%20dilemma%20of%20the%20judge%2C%20which%20may%20be%20rare%2C%20has%20to%20take%20into%20account%20the%20delicate%20balance%20which%20the%20constitutional%20court%20or%20courts%20of%20law%20have%20to%20strike%20between%20the%20law%20and%20its%20strict%20application%20and%20the%20repercussion%20of%20its%20judgments%20and%20orders%20by%20application%20of%20such%20laws%20on%20the%20society%20as%20a%20whole%20and%20the%20individuals%20who%20are%20before%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20cancelled%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20against%20the%20man%20in%202015%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20kidnapping%20and%20raping%20the%20girl%2C%20who%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20a%20major%20while%20the%20police%20maintained%20that%20she%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20in%20case%20the%20FIR%20is%20not%20quashed%20it%20will%20result%20in%20affecting%20the%20future%20of%20the%20couple's%20two%20daughters%20resulting%20in%20failure%20of%20effective%20and%20real%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20eloping%2C%20the%20couple%20got%20married%20as%20per%20Muslim%20rites%20and%20ceremonies%20and%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20man's%20parents.%20An%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20the%20man%20by%20the%20girl's%20father%20and%20when%20the%20police%20caught%20hold%20of%20them%2C%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20five%20months%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20maintained%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20she%20loved%20and%20married%20the%20man%20and%20had%20voluntarily%20entered%20into%20a%20consensual%20relationship%20with%20him%20and%20that%20she%20was%2018%20years%20of%20age%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20couple%20entered%20into%20a%20marital%20union%20even%20though%20the%20law%20did%20not%20permit%20them%20to%20do%20so%20and%20the%20girl%20supported%20the%20man's%20case%20at%20every%20stage%20and%20not%20that%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20have%20now%20been%20married%20for%20about%20nine%20years%20and%20have%20been%20blessed%20with%20two%20daughters%20and%20are%20happily%20raising%20their%20children%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20future%20of%20the%20families%20of%20the%20parties%2C%20the%20two%20daughters%20and%20the%20wife%20who%20is%20a%20house-maker%20and%20their%20beautiful%20harmonious%20life%20they%20have%20built%20together%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20is%20at%20stake%20and%20dependent%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20this%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20notes%20that%20the%20judicial%20system%20is%20tasked%20not%20only%20with%20interpreting%20and%20upholding%20the%20law%20but%20also%20with%20understanding%20the%20dynamics%20of%20society.%20The%20court's%20role%20extends%20beyond%20a%20mere%20application%20and%20interpretation%20of%20statutes.%20It%20involves%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20implications%20of%20its%20decisions%20on%20individuals%20and%20the%20community%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20when%20the%20scales%20of%20justice%20have%20to%20be%20weighed%2C%20they%20are%20not%20always%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20mathematical%20precision%20or%20mathematical%20formulas%2C%20but%20at%20times%2C%20while%20one%20side%20of%20the%20scale%20carries%20the%20law%2C%20the%20other%20side%20may%20carry%20the%20entire%20life%2C%20happiness%20and%20future%20of%20toddlers%2C%20their%20parents%20and%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20that%20reflects%20and%20portrays%20such%20pure%20happiness%20sans%20any%20criminality%20will%20definitely%20equal%20the%20scale%20carrying%20law%20as%20the%20application%20of%20law%20is%20meant%20for%20maintaining%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20th