%2C%20which%20is%20functioning%20as%20the%20legal%20arm%20of%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20utterly%20distorted%20the%20reality%20in%20Gaza%20following%20the%20October%207%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F82EfD9WeuF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F82EfD9WeuF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Lior%20Haiat%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B1%20(%40LiorHaiat)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiorHaiat%2Fstatus%2F1745427037039280207%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Jeremy%20Corbyn%2C%20a%20British%20member%20of%20parliament%20and%20a%20former%20leader%20of%20the%20main%20opposition%20Labour%20Party%2C%20has%20told%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20The%20Hague%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Israel%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20strong%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20brilliantly%20prepared%20and%20put%20forward%2C%20analytical%2C%20non-sensational%20and%20minimalist%20in%20terms%20of%20images%20that%20were%20shown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorbyn%20also%20said%20that%20he%20hopes%20the%20interim%20injunction%20that%20was%20requested%20by%20the%20South%20African%20lawyers%20today%20will%20come%20soon%20%E2%80%9Cif%20international%20law%20is%20to%20mean%20anything%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20anything%20would%20change%20even%20if%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20request%20is%20successful%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20is%20incremental.%20Every%20time%20you%20step%20out%20on%20the%20street%20and%20wave%20a%20Palestinian%20flag%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Stop%20the%20killing%20of%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99%2C%20any%20time%20someone%20speaks%20up%20in%20a%20parliament%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20incremental%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20spokesperson%20Sami%20Abu%20Zuhri%20t