%20boards%20are%20ready%20to%20play%20one%20another%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20government%20clearance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zaka%20Ashraf%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcb.com.pk%2Fround-up-detail%2Fzaka-ashraf-naila-bhatti-and-salman-naseer-hold-press-conference-at-gaddafi-stadium.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epcb.com.pk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20official%20website%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethere%20has%20been%20no%20reaction%20from%20the%20BCCI%20after%20this%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Sepetmber%2C%202023%2C%20Union%20Sports%20Minsters%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20that%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20had%20earlier%20decided%20a%20bilateral%20series%20of%20cricket%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20wouldn't%20take%20place%20until%20Pakistan%20puts%20end%20to%20%26quot%3Bterrorism%26quot%3B.%20Anurag%20Thakur%20while%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBCCI%20had%20decided%20much%20earlier%20that%20we%20would%20not%20play%20bilateral%20matches%20with%20Pakistan%20until%20they%20put%20an%20end%20to%20terrorism%2C%20cross-border%20attacks%20and%20infiltration.%20I%20think%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20country%20and%20of%20the%20public%20are%20also%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20came%20after%20three%20top%20Indian%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20gunfight%20in%20Anantnag's%20encounter%20with%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20which%20has%20enraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20recently%20played%20Pakistan%20at%20the%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20India%20won%20the%20match%20by%20seven%20wickets.%20They%20will%20next%20face%20each%20other%20in%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20in%20New%20York%20on%20June%209.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704982560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2