not%20stand%20for%20so%20long%20and%20some%20of%20my%20friends%20suggested%20starting%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20way%20I%20could%20reach%20more%20people%20and%20everyone%20could%20have%20their%20own%20gardens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20she%20started%20her%20YouTube%20channel%20Patnam%20Lo%20Palleturu%20by%20Pinnaka%20Padma%20and%20has%20over%204%20Lakh%20subscribers.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20videos%20are%20well-liked%20by%20many%20people%20and%20they%20keep%20getting%20viewed.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20my%20routine%20to%20make%20a%20video%20whenever%20I%20learn%20something%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPadma%20shares%20that%20she%20successfully%20grew%20microgreens%20in%20the%20US%20while%20she%20was%20visiting%20her%20children%20and%20hosted%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304873%2Fkerala-man-grows-microgreens-superfood-at-home-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrogreens%20dinner.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20many%20platforms%20have%20applauded%20her%20spirit%20and%20awarded%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20an%20award%20from%20Social%20Woods%20for%20innovation%20in%20urban%20farming%20and%20another%20one%20from%20Hyderabad%20Greater%20Municipal%20Panchayat%20Raj%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Padma%20has%20received%20awards%20for%20her%20innovations%20in%20urban%20farming.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fmedical-equipment-8-1704979989-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338060%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPadma%20has%20received%20awards%20for%20her%20innovations%20in%20urban%20farming.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Padma%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20her%20journey%2C%20Padma%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20you%20cannot%20do%20if%20you%20have%20the%20passion%20and%20love%20to%20do%20it.%20I%20find%20joy%20in%20sharing%20and%20planting.%20Whenever%20I%20distribute%20my%20produce%20among%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20it%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20accomplishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20expresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704980802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338048%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20terrace%20gardening%20tips%3F%20Hyderabad's%20Padma%20turned%20her%20terrace%20garden%20into%20a%20blooming%20green%20oasis%20with%20over%20a%20thousand%20plants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338048%2Fterrace-garden-tips-by-hyderabad-woman-grows-organic-vegetables-at-home%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20Win%20In%20Bangladesh%20And%20What%20It%20Means%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20party%20Awami%20League%20has%20won%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20general%20elections.%20This%20is%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20fifth%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20Opposition%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20(BNP)%20led%20by%20former%20PM%20Khaleda%20Zia%20boycotted%20the%20elections.%20Zia%20was%20arrested%20for%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B%20activities%20just%20before%20the%20elections%20after%20she%20demanded%20that%20Hasina%20step%20down%20to%20make%20way%20for%20a%20neutral%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20voter%20turnout%20is%20also%20controversial.%20The%20official%20figure%20is%2040%20per%20cent%20but%20reports%20suggest%20it%20could%20be%20less%20than%2028%20per%20cent.%20The%20turnout%20on%20the%20dashboard%20at%20the%20election%20body%20headquarters%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20press%20briefing%2C%20was%2028%20per%20cent%20according%20to%20a%20widely%20shared%20screenshot%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20BNP%20has%20rejected%20the%20elections%20as%20'dummy%20polls'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20voting%20day%20passed%20off%20peacefully%2C%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections%20saw%20violent%20protests%20and%20deadly%20arson.%20The%20government%20accused%20the%20BNP%20of%20inciting%20violence%20to%20sabotage%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20January%207%20elections%20were%20not%20free%20and%20fair%20and%20riddled%20with%20irregularities.%20Critics%20have%20also%20cautioned%20against%20the%20virtual%20one-party%20rule%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20party%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20Opposition.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20of%20the%20BNP%20to%20abstain%20from%20elections%20is%20their%20party's%20strategic%20choice.%20The%20BNP%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20political%20violence%20and%20arson%20since%20October%2028.%20A%20democratic%20government%20can't%20just%20sit%20and%20watch.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20and%20property%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20government%20had%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20take%20action%20against%20such%20terrorism%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Syed%20Borhan%20Kabir%2C%20chief%20editor%2C%20Bangla%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%20that%20if%20the%20BNP%20had%20participated%20in%20elections%2C%20democracy%20would%20be%20complete%2C%20and%20the%20election%20would%20have%20been%20competitive.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20voter%20turnout%20is%20always%20low.%20Nevertheless%2C%2041%20per%20cent%20of%20voters%20have%20cast%20their%20votes%2C%20which%20is%20not%20bad.%20A%20weak%20constitutional%20government%20is%20much%20better%20than%20an%20unconstitutional%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBurgeoning%20India-Bangladesh%20Partnership%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20has%20always%20accepted%20India's%20role%20in%20its%20independence%20in%201971.%20The%20two%20countries%20share%20a%20common%20history%20and%20heritage%2C%20linguistic%20and%20cultural%20ties.%20They%20share%20a%20unique%20geographical%20feature%20-%20not%20only%20is%20Bangladesh%20surrounded%20by%20India%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20but%20they%20share%2054%20rivers%20between%20them%2C%20which%20flow%20from%20the%20Himalayas%20to%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20With%20so%20many%20similarities%2C%20people-to-people%20ties%20and%20development%20cooperation%20have%20taken%20precedence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20there%20have%20been%20periods%20of%20mutual%20distrust.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kabir%20explains%20that%20after%201975%2C%20due%20to%20emerging%20anti-India%20sentiments%20and%20a%20shift%20towards%20Pakistan-centric%20politics%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20there%20was%20a%20period%20of%20strained%20relations%2C%20and%20Bangladesh's%20territory%20was%20sometimes%20used%20to%20target%20India.%20%26quot%3BIn%202009%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20adopted%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20terrorism.%20The%20rise%20of%20separatist%20elements%20is%20not%20something%20India%20desires.%20Concurrently%2C%20the%20mutual%20trust%20and%20confidence%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20strengthened%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20resentment%20in%20Bangladesh%20against%20the%20failed%20agreement%20to%20share%20Teesta%20River%20water%2C%20which%20was%20to%20be%20signed%20in%20September%202011.%20The%20anxiety%20over%20transboundary%20effects%20of%20the%20proposed%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20and%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sporadic%20incidents%20of%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20being%20shot%20at%20on%20the%20border%2C%20are%20issues%20that%20rankle%20with%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20a%20balance%20of%20trade%20skewed%20in%20favour%20of%20India%2C%20the%20large%20volume%20of%20informal%20trade%2C%20again%20dominated%20by%20India%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20trade%20deficit%20and%20Bangladesh%20expects%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20to%20resolve%20these%20matters.%20According%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%2C%20Indian%20exports%20to%20Bangladesh%20between%20April%20and%20October%202023%20declined%20by%2013.32%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20imports%20saw%20a%20smaller%202.3%20per%20cent%20dip.%20This%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20Bangladesh's%20forex%20shortages%20and%20liquidity%20crunch%20and%20maybe%20election-related%20slowdown%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20at%20stronger%20momentum%20in%20bilateral%20partnership%2C%20there%20can't%20be%20better%20news%20than%20PM%20Hasina's%20win.%20To%20iron%20out%20concerns%2C%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20had%20foreign%20secretary-level%20talks%20on%20key%20areas%20such%20as%20security%2C%20trade%20and%20regional%20connectivity.%20The%20two%20sides%20also%20discussed%20the%20river%20Teesta%20dispute%20and%20other%20water-sharing%20treaties%20last%20November.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20values%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20this%20was%20demonstrated%20when%20PM%20Hasina%20was%20the%20only%20South%20Asian%20leader%20invited%20to%20the%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit%20under%20India's%20presidency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20ties%2C%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20recently%20inaugurated%20three%20projects%2C%20the%20Akhaura-%20Agartala%20Cross-Border%20Rail%20Link%2C%20Khulna-Mongla%20Port%20Rail%20Line%2C%20and%20Unit-II%20of%20the%20Maitree%20Super%20Critical%20Thermal%20Power%20Plant%20in%20Rampal%2C%20Bangladesh.%20These%20projects%20are%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20connectivity%20and%20energy%20security%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20Bangladesh%20government%20has%20also%20allowed%20the%20transit%20and%20trans-shipment%20of%20cargo%20from%20West%20Bengal%20to%20the%20northeastern%20states%20via%20Chattogram%20and%20Mongla%20ports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20ongoing%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20for%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20promote%20economic%20ties.%20Under%20CEPA%20(Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement)%2C%20the%20two%20trading%20partners%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20or%20eliminate%20customs%20duties%20on%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20goods%20traded%20between%20them.%20Last%20year%2C%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20initiated%20trade%20transactions%20in%20rupees%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20the%20US%20dollar%20and%20strengthen%20the%20regional%20currency%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20are%20at%20their%20peak.%20In%20the%20short%20term%2C%20there%20will%20be%20business%20as%20usual%20but%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20if%20no%20concrete%20agreements%20are%20signed%2C%20people%20will%20see%20through%20it.%20Water%20sharing%20has%20always%20been%20an%20emotive%20issue%20for%20the%20common%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sreeradha%20Datta%2C%20professor%20of%20International%20Affairs%2C%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20feel%20that%20they%20have%20supported%20India%20in%20opening%20their%20trade%20corridor%20and%20facilitating%20cross-border%20bilateral%20engagement.%20It's%20high%20time%20for%20India%20to%20reciprocate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ms%20Datta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%20need%20each%20other%20to%20survive%20and%20thrive.%20Radicalisation%20is%20a%20common%20enemy%20and%20only%20a%20joint%20fight%20will%20help.%20Lessons%20in%20geopolitics%20point%20towards%20countries%20forging%20mutually%20beneficial%20relationships.%20There%20is%20no%20guideline%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704980520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3bjks7os_sheikh-hasina_625x300_07_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsheikh-hasinas-win-in-bangladesh-and-what-it-means-for-india-4843408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20party%20Awami%20League%20has%20won%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20term%20in%20general%20elections.%20This%20is%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20fifth%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsheikh-hasinas-win-in-bangladesh-and-what-it-means-for-india-4843408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsheikh-hasinas-win-in-bangladesh-and-what-it-means-for-india-4843408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22ht