20Ducks%20Mention%20of%20Shankaracharyas%20Critical%20of%26nbsp%3BPoliticisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11173806%2FEffect-62.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20deployed%20Union%20ministers%20and%20state%20chief%20ministers%20to%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20of%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20and%20being%20%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20invoked%20the%20party%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9CNehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20and%20not%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20announced%20its%20decision%20to%20decline%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20being%20planned%20for%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20January%2011%2C%20BJP%20MP%20and%20national%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20invoked%20former%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20shows%20that%20the%20party%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9CGandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%2C%20this%20is%20not%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress.%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20political%20view%20was%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20he%20used%20to%20sing%20%E2%80%98Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20samadhi%20(cremation%20spot)%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99%20is%20written.%20Today%20that%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20being%20started%20with%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20and%20Congress%20is%20not%20attending.%20This%20makes%20it%20very%20clear%20the%20difference%20between%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%20that%20its%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20party%20chief%20M