20Lord%20Ram%20and%20questioned%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20reached%20the%20heights%20of%20appeasement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Smriti%20Irani%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%20face%20has%20become%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%20party%E2%80%99s%20anti-Lord%20Ram%20face%20is%20before%20the%20nation.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20party%20that%20had%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20court%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20does%20not%20have%20an%20identity.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%2C%20INDI%20Alliance%20has%20insulted%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20time%20and%20again.%20Now%2C%20the%20declining%20of%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98pran%20pratishtha%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20shows%20their%20anti-Sanatan%20mindset%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Irani%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20%26amp%3B%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20declining%20the%20invitation%20to%20%E2%80%98pranpratishtha%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20party%E2%80%99s%20anti-Lord%20Ram%20face%20is%20before%20the%20nation.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20under%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHKG9WUpapw%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHKG9WUpapw%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsaoDQFOT4e%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FsaoDQFOT4e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%