%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbad-hijab-using-makeup-taliban-lash-detain-afghan-girls-for-violating-dress-code%2Famp_articleshow%2F106727640.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Biren%20Singh%20Opening%20a%20New%20Front'%3A%20Manipur%20Govt's%20Possible%20Rethink%20on%20ST%20Status%20to%20Kukis%20Draws%20Ire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20as%20violence%20continues%20to%20rage%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisations%20have%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20after%20Singh%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20considering%20setting%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20rethink%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20of%20the%20Kukis%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkukis-cm-biren-singh-new-front-escalate-conflict-govt-rethink-st-status-9103934%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20such%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuse%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%E2%80%9D%20their%20community%20will%20further%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20January%209%2C%20came%20in%20response%20to%20queries%20on%20a%20representation%20made%20to%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20tribal%20affairs%20by%20the%20Meitei%20leader%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20Maheshwar%20Thounaojam%2C%20for%20the%20exclusion%20of%20Kukis%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list.%20Thounaojam%20holds%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(Kukis)%20are%20not%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Centre%20forwarded%20the%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20as%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20is%C2%A0a%20prerequisite%20to%20process%20any%20such%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20that%20an%20all-tribe%20committee%20would%20be%20formed%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20Chin%20Kuki%20community%20would%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%20of%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20included%20in%20the%20(ST)%20list%20of%20Manipur%20but%20how%20they%20were%20included%20needs%20to%20be%20re-examined.%20Before%20commenting%2C%20we%20have%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20consisting%20of%20all%20tribes%20(of%20the%20state)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fall-tribe-panel-to-be-formed-to-decide-if-chin-kukis-will-remain-st-manipur-cm%2Farticle67724832.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20is%20a%20collective%20name%20of%20various%20tribes%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Chin%20is%20one%20of%20those.%20The%20Chin%20community%20people%20also%20share%20ethnicity%20with%20the%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%20and%20a%20section%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20neighbouring%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20exception%20to%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20a%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisation%20based%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20accused%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%E2%80%9D%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Manipur%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%20overtly%20and%20covertly%20supports%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20current%20ethnic%20conflict.%20The%20communal%20Biren%20Singh%20administration%20has%20now%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20by%20pushing%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20ITLF%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20further%20attempts%20by%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20use%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20will%20only%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20be%20detrimental%20to%20him%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20Inpi%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20called%20on%20the%20state%20government%20to%20stop%20any%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Calter%20the%20ST%20status%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%9D%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20Inpi%20Sadar%20Hills%20vehemently%20condemns%20any%20attempt%20to%20erase%20the%20Kuki%20community%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20as%20it%20blatantly%20violates%20the%20principles%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20the%20Constitutional%20safeguards%20provided%20to%20tribal%20communities%20but%20also%20perpetuate%20injustice%20and%20discrimination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kuki%20Inpi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%20last%20year%20and%20over%20180%20people%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203%20after%20a%20%E2%80%98Tribal%20Solidarity%20March%E2%80%99%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%C2%A0Meiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%25%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20live%20mostly%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%2C%20while%20tribals%2C%20which%20include%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%2C%20constitute%2040%25%20and%20reside%20mainly%20in%20the%20hill%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704966274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbiren-singh-opening-a-new-front-manipur-govts-possible-rethink-on-st-status-to-kukis-draws-ire%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20said%20his%20government%20is%20considering%20setting%20up%20an%20all-tribe%20committee%20to%20decide%20if%20Kukis%20remain%20under%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Kuki%20outfits%20say%20the%20move%20would%20further%20escalate%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbiren-singh-opening-a-new-front-manipur-govts-possible-rethink-on-st-status-to-kukis-draws-ire%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22United%20Airlines%20flight%20makes%20emergency%20landing%20after%20'open%20door%20light%20turns%20on'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704966000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-airbus-united-airlines_6418051.jpg%3F20240111095003%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Funited-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-florida-after-open-door-light-turns-on-13046001%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20United%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Sarasota%2C%20Florida%2C%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20the%20same%20state%20shortly%20after%20take-off%2C%20reportedly%20due%20to%20an%20open%20door%20light%20illuminating%20in%20mid-air.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Funited-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-florida-after-open-door-light-turns-on-13046001%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Funited-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-florida-after-open-door-light-turns-on-13046001%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Funited-airlines-flight-makes-emergency-landing-in-florida-after-open-door-light-turns-on-13046001%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20the%20US%20Enters%20Election%20Year%2C%20Will%20There%20Be%20a%20Peaceful%20Transfer%20of%20Power%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11140034%2FEffect-61.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20enters%202024%20with%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20foreboding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Republican%20primaries%20loom%20to%20find%20their%20nominee%20for%20the%20November%20presidential%20election%2C%20US%20politics%20hits%20new%20lows.%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20CV%20plumbs%20new%20depths%20as%20several%20states%20are%20contemplating%20barring%20him%20from%20the%20primaries%20altogether%2C%20on%20the%20charge%20of%20insurrection%2C%20while%20Maine%20and%20Colorado%20have%20already%20excluded%20him%20from%20the%20ballot.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-the-sc-rule-in-trumps-favour-to-keep-his-presidential-ambitions-alive%5C%22%3EUS%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20ultimately%20have%20to%20rule%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20uncharted%20territory%20other%20than%20after%20the%20Civil%20War%20that%20ended%20in%201865%2C%20when%20the%20constitution%20was%20amended%20to%20prevent%20former%20insurrectionist%20Confederate%20States%E2%80%99%20officials%20from%20taking%20public%20office.%20Add%20that%20onto%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20accomplishments%20%E2%80%93%20twice%20impeached%2C%20facing%2091%20indictments%20including%20for%20insurrection%20and%20election%20interference%2C%20and%20court%20battles%20over%20sexual%20attacks.%20His%20violent%20speeches%20%E2%80%93%20invoking%20Hitlerite%20language%20of%20%E2%80%9Cblood%20poisoning%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvermin%E2%80%9D%20with%20regard%20to%20immigrants%2C%20minorities%2C%20refugees%2C%20liberals%2C%20and%20the%20Left%20%E2%80%93%20add%20to%20the%20sense%20of%20foreboding.%20He%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfighting%20like%20hell%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20refuses%20to%20believe%20that%20he%20could%20lose%20the%20election%20other%20than%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjanuary-6-us-capitol-attack-deep-state-conspiracies-havent-gone-away%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cdeep%20state%E2%80%9D%20conspiracies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20such%20conditions%20and%20forces%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjanuary-6-us-capitol-attack-deep-state-conspiracies-havent-gone-away%5C%22%3EJanuary%206%20US%20Capitol%20Attack%3A%20Deep%20State%20Conspiracies%20Haven%E2%80%99t%20Gone%C2%A0Away%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%20%E2%80%93%20half%20the%20world%20is%20voting%20this%20year%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%202024%20US%20election%20rubs%20shoulders%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brunswickgroup.com%2Feight-key-elections-to-watch-in-2024-i25831%2F%5C%22%3Eworldwide%20wave%20of%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20States%20representing%20billions%20of%20people%20and%20around%2050%25%20of%20world%20GDP%20are%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20this%20year.%20Many%20states%20face%20potentially%20volatile%20election%20processes%20in%20geopolitically%20fraught%20times%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20widespread%20domestic%20volatility%20%E2%80%93%20UK%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20India%2C%20UK%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Russia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20those%20global%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20UK%2C%20EU%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20India%2C%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20a%20direct%20impact%20or%20at%20least%20implications%20for%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20regarding%20geopolitical%20rivalries%20(attitudes%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20military%20aid%20for%20example%3B%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20posture%20towards%20Beijing%20and%20the%20US%3B%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20resolution)%2C%20and%20the%20prospects%20for%20international%20economic%20coordination.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20spiralling%20into%20a%20regional%20war%2C%20impact%20and%20implicate%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20regional%20power.%20The%20only%20superpower%20that%20is%20virtually%20omnipresent%2C%20to%20which%20everywhere%20is%20a%20national%20interest.%20The%20privileges%20of%20full%20spectrum%20dominance%20and%20forward%20power%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20for%20President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20bid%20are%20increasingly%20bleak%20as%20national%20polls%20show%20Trump%20leading%20the%20incumbent%2C%20and%20as%20Arab%20and%20Muslim-Americans%20develop%20campaigns%20against%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20blocking%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20resolution%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Though%20they%20are%20a%20very%20small%20minority%20of%20the%20US%20population%20and%20electorate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fcampaign%2F4356645-arab-muslim-americans-could-abandon-biden-democrats-warn-advocates%2F%5C%22%3EMuslim-Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20tilt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20within%20swing%20states%20towards%20Donald%20Trump.%20As%20ominously%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Ffor-biden-youth-vote-polling-is-a-warning-not-the-apocalypse%2F%5C%22%3Evoters%20under%2035%20years%20of%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20much%20larger%20slice%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20who%20supported%20Biden%20by%20large%20margins%20in%202020%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20deserting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-