Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20privilege%20I%20have%20had%20till%20September%203%2C%202023.%20I%20have%20offered%20accompaniment%20to%20the%20vocals%20of%20Ustad%20Rashid%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Esahab%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20countless%20concerts%20spanning%20the%20last%2026%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20bhai%20always%20loved%20and%20respected%20me%20like%20a%20younger%20brother.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20have%20always%20been%20like%20a%20member%20of%20his%20family.%20Love%20and%20respect%20for%20Rashid%20bhai%20will%20always%20remain%20in%20my%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20like%20Rashid%20bhai%2C%20a%20distinguished%20artist%20and%20exceptional%20human%20being%20with%20an%20unmatched%20personality%2C%20are%20rare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllah%20had%20not%20only%20blessed%20him%20with%20spiritual%20and%20musical%20beauty%20but%20also%20a%20calm%20heart%20and%20cheerful%20countenance.%20I%20always%20found%20him%20helping%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20Bhai%E2%80%99s%20demise%20has%20brought%20sorrow%20not%20only%20to%20Hindustan%20but%20to%20artists%20all%20around%20the%20world.%20No%20one%20can%20replace%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20a%20thousand%20years%20the%20daffodil%20weeps%20for%20an%20eye%20to%20behold%20it%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnly%20once%20in%20an%20epoch%20is%20born%20a%20person%20who%20sees%20its%20beauty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20pray%20that%20Allah%20gives%20him%20the%20highest%20place%20in%20heaven%2C%20and%20gives%20courage%20to%20his%20family%20members%20in%20this%20difficult%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMurad%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20a%20sarangi%20player%20and%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20celebrated%20musicians.%20He%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20Siddiqi%20Ahmed%20Khan%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Ghulam%20Sabir%20Khan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Hindi%20original%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704955020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp