achine%20was%20up%20and%20running.%20Currently%2C%20our%20company%20operates%20entirely%20on%20automated%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20proudly%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20machine%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20the%20outer%20cover%20and%20the%20filling.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20the%20filling%20goes%20through%20a%20meticulous%20process%20from%20cutting%20to%20washing.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20take%20the%20example%20of%20a%20vegetable%20%3Cem%3Emomo%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20prepared.%20All%20the%20veggies%20arrive%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20then%20the%20cutting%20process%20is%20automated.%20Various%20machines%2C%20ranging%20from%20dicing%20to%20shredding%2C%20handle%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20automated%20cutting%2C%20the%20veggies%20are%20washed%20and%20transferred%20to%20a%20cooking%20wok.%20We%20use%20an%20automated%20cooking%20wok%20%E2%80%94%20a%20robotic%20wok%2C%20essentially%20%E2%80%94%20to%20cook%20the%20filling.%20Multiple%20woks%20are%20operated%20simultaneously%20to%20meet%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20phase%2C%20Shouvik%20explains%20that%20the%20focus%20shifts%20to%20dough%20processing%2C%20with%20the%20dough%20being%20prepared%20in%20a%20vacuum%20dough%20mixer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20specialised%20equipment%20that%20ensures%20even%20mixing%20by%20creating%20a%20vacuum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dough%20and%20filling%20are%20prepared%2C%20the%20dough%20is%20fed%20into%20a%20forming%20machine%2C%20where%20it%20is%20taken%20in%2C%20and%20the%20filling%20is%20loaded%20onto%20a%20filling%20hopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20machines%20work%20automatically%20to%20shape%20the%20%3Cem%3Emomos%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Each%20production%20line%20consists%20of%20three%20different%20units%2C%20and%20each%20line%20can%20produce%20around%208%2C000%20pieces%20in%20an%20hour.%20Each%20machine%20can%20produce%202.25%20lakh%20%3Cem%3Emomos%20%3C%2F